To start, execute "neap" or "neap -h"

Check https://github.com/vzxwco/neap
for the latest release, documentation and sample config file.


Hotkey
======

By installing `python-keybinder2` switching desktops with hotkeys is enabled.

To set hotkeys, add section `[neap_hotkey]` to your `.neaprc` and add values
like `hotkey_up = <Ctrl>Up`.
